title: Sokoa Azkarate
text: Sokoa Azkarate is a Spanish former <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="goalkeeper%20%28soccer%29">goalkeeper</a> who played mainly for <a href="Real%20Sociedad%20%28women%29">Real Sociedad</a> in the <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Spanish First Division</a>, where she competed for the position with the younger <a href="Cris%20Cornejo">Cris Cornejo</a> until retiring in 2014 aged 35. Prior to playing football, she was a <a href="basketball">basketball</a> player for five years.
